\end{aligned}
\label{eq:prob2flavorexpanded}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where for simplicity 
\begin_inset Formula $c=\cos(\theta)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $s=\sin(\theta)$
\end_inset

.
 Evaluating all inner products and simplifying terms in 
